        "commit_message": "`__Pyx__Coroutine_NewInit()` does not initialize `monitoring_states` and `monitoring_version`\non the generator object. Since `PyObject_GC_New()` does not zero memory, these contain\ngarbage when first read by `PyMonitoring_EnterScope()` via `__Pyx__TraceStartGen()`.\n\nThe fix zero-initializes both fields at construction, consistent with how `__Pyx_TraceStartFunc`\nalready handles regular functions.",
